Title: Lorentz and CPT Violating Chern-Simons Term in the Formulation of
  Functional Integral
Authors: J.-M. Chung
Comments: 5 pages, no figure, RevTex
Report-no: MIT-CTP-2853
Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D60 (1999) 127901
\\
  We show that in the functional integral formalism the (finite) coefficient of
the induced, Lorentz- and CPT-violating Chern-Simons term, arising from the
Lorentz- and CPT-violating fermion sector, is undetermined.
